title: Untitled
description: Xander wants to have some fun, but no one else in CFD wants to play. Tera’s taking a nap. Lucy isn’t feeling well.Ben and Nicole are nowhere to be found.Jesse’s not quite up to playing. Kennedy’s off doing his own thing.Jace and Summer are on a trip with the kids.And Sera… well she’s in a bad way.  It’s a good thing Xander always has a bigger plan… this one includes some fans!
author: Anne Mercier
